{"id":728,"date":"2021-05-10T12:19:59","date_gmt":"2021-05-10T12:19:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/?page_id=728"},"modified":"2022-09-26T14:59:27","modified_gmt":"2022-09-26T14:59:27","slug":"foss4g-asia","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/foss4g-asia\/","title":{"rendered":"FOSS4G &#8211; ASIA"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong>FOSS4G-ASIA<\/strong> conference series started in 2014. The first edition of FOSS4G-Asia in Bangkok, Thailand. Since then, it is being held every two years in different Asian countries. All work related to the hosting of the conference is done by the local organizing committee work that is formed by the local hosting institution \/ organizers. The conference has now become the main Asian FOSS4G event.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-medium-font-size has-vivid-red-color\"><strong>FOSS4G ASIA 2014 &#8211; BANGKOK<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\" style=\"grid-template-columns: 21% auto;\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.foss4g-asia.org\/2014\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"187\" height=\"187\" class=\"wp-image-730\" src=\"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2014-LOGO.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2014-LOGO.png 187w, https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2014-LOGO-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 187px) 100vw, 187px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">The first Free &amp; Open Solutions for Geoinformatics-Asia conference was held in Bangkok, Thailand from the 2<sup>nd<\/sup> to 5th December 2014 at Asian Institute of Technology (AIT), Thailand. The major theme of the conference was \u2018<em>Enabling Geospatial Asia through Open and Participatory ICT Ecosystem\u2019.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-medium-font-size has-vivid-red-color\"><strong>FOSS4G ASIA 2017 &#8211; HYDERABAD<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\" style=\"grid-template-columns: 23% auto;\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.foss4g-asia.org\/2017\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"173\" height=\"173\" class=\"wp-image-734\" src=\"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2017-LOGO.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2017-LOGO.png 173w, https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2017-LOGO-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 173px) 100vw, 173px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">The second FOSS4G ASIA Conference was held in 2017, Hyderabad, India from January 26-29, 2017, Hyderabad, India and hosted by IIIT-Hyderabad, India. The major theme of the conference was <em>\u2018Empowering communities through open geospatial innovation\u2019. <\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-medium-font-size has-vivid-red-color\"><strong>FOSS4G ASIA 2018 \u2013 MORATUWA<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\" style=\"grid-template-columns: 21% auto;\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.foss4g-asia.org\/2018\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"411\" height=\"371\" class=\"wp-image-736\" src=\"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2018-LOGO.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2018-LOGO.png 411w, https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/F4G-ASIA-2018-LOGO-300x271.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 411px) 100vw, 411px\" \/><\/a><\/figure>\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">The third FOSS4G-Asia was conducted at the Department of Town &amp; Country Planning, University of Moratuwa, Sri Lanka from <strong>2<sup>nd<\/sup> <\/strong>to 5<sup>th<\/sup>&nbsp;December 2018. The overall theme for the conference was <strong>\u2018<\/strong><em>Open Source for Sustainable Development\u2019<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>FOSS4G-ASIA conference series started in 2014. The first edition of FOSS4G-Asia in Bangkok, Thailand. Since then, it is being held every two years in different Asian countries. All work related to the hosting of the conference is done by the local organizing committee work that is formed by the local hosting institution \/ organizers. The [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":9,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/728"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/9"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=728"}],"version-history":[{"count":19,"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/728\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2057,"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/728\/revisions\/2057"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/foss4g.asia\/2021\